{"tid":81731,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人分享下中英字典APP?","createTime":"2017-01-15T14:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T16:30:33.000Z","uid":64376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b244130fd01c4a0cf04b4281acfe56821aff4d","tid":81731,"uid":64376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"我部字典機就黎壞，想買部平板再裝返個APP代替，唔知各位有無推薦，分享下使用情況都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想有以下功能：<br />\n1) 英美音標+發音 (最緊要呢樣)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2) 全句翻譯<br />\n3) 過往記錄<br />\n4) 不斷更新新詞彙<br />\n5) 漢英字典<br />\n6) 多同義反義例句<br />\n7) 每日新字<br />\n<br />\n其實我有打算買朗文個當代英語字典，不過係google play睇到d評價唔太好，所以想問下各位意見。付費app我都ok<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d9eacd034ab628b53e313b4a2e0b2898a35f98","tid":81731,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T14:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95bfaccc4a2b04ba6cfb03c664f6b1c5516b64c9","tid":81731,"uid":1103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"Erudite"},{"pid":"437272458cc2b5fd338bfba5ea72e11cb37ddacb","tid":81731,"uid":1103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Erudite</blockquote><br />\nNo thanks"},{"pid":"405b23142ee5e5e9e9bedf43dc12b7599cb4edb4","tid":81731,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7db233d2b8b9b3233109aefe5cde7be18c3034a0","tid":81731,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:11:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a891f5cf13edd019cfd72b7530870496a9a7d42a","tid":81731,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:15:50.000Z","msg":"唔介意支那野 可以試下有道"},{"pid":"2473a49ba5dfdb43060223d16089ea4cfee9fdeb","tid":81731,"uid":21181